- Plots:
  1) Elbow (k=1..50) + two zoom panels (7–15, 25–35)  [NO red knee lines]
  2) PCA biplot (PC1 vs PC2) with channel loadings as arrows, legend only

Outputs:
- KPM(08132025)_elbow_k1-50_pub_with_zooms.pdf / .png
- KPM(08132025)_pca_biplot_channels_pub_legendonly.pdf / .png
"""

